name: Master of Dark Magic
effect:
2 cards whose names are, or that mention, "Dark Magician" or "Magician of Black Chaos", including at least 1 Fusion or Ritual Monster
Must first be Fusion Summoned by returning the above cards from your hand or field to the Deck (you do not use "Polymerization"), and cannot be Fusion Summoned by other ways.
You can only Special Summon "Master of Dark Magic" once per turn.
This card is treated as "Magician of Black Chaos" while on the field or in the Graveyard.
If this card is Special Summoned: You can add 1 Spell Card from your Deck to your hand that mentions "Dark Magician" or "Magician of Black Chaos" in its text.
During your turn (Quick Effect): You can banish up to 2 cards your opponent controls.
You can only use this effect of "Master of Dark Magic" once per turn.
